h. Management considers the provisions of COA Circular No. 2020-006 dated January 31, 2020 which provides for the guidelines and procedures in the conduct of physical count of PPE, recognition of PPE items found at station and disposition for non-existing/missing PPE items, for the one-time cleansing of PPE account balances of government agencies.

